{"tid":1182380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC首用華為5G直播 不到1分鐘就斷線","createTime":"2019-06-02T06:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T12:07:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8dcb8c89a0303dfe6273ae9c338bfc9af7837de2","tid":1182380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:45:39.000Z","msg":"英國廣播公司（BBC）日前首次使用中國華為（Huawei）5G網路進行現場直播，不過卻在直播開始後不到1分鐘出現嚴重「LAG（延遲）」，最終在不得已情況下，以中斷直播收場。而導致BBC 5G直播中斷的原因，BBC稱，是因直播數據流量太大，導致開始直播時就用盡流量所致。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，BBC上週（5月30日）進行英國歷史性首次商用5G網路直播。BBC的記者Rory Cellan Jones在直播前於Twitter分享幕後花絮，並拍攝有華為商標的5G網路設備，表示：「就是這個設備（華為5G設備）能夠支持我們進行BBC首次5G電視直播。」<br />\n<br />\n不料，就在BBC直播開始後的40秒時，影片就出現嚴重LAG的情況，並在約10秒之後變成「有聲無畫」，BBC最後在迫不得已情況下，決定中斷直播。<br />\n<br />\n外界好奇，導致BBC 5G直播中斷的原因。Rory Cellan Jones在其Twitter發文表示，是因為直播數據流量太大，導致開始直播時就已用盡流量所造成的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2809767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809767&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=5366f35a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809767&h=583fc4e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2809767</a>"},{"pid":"b7571544d2400bf58a32999639efbffb324a510a","tid":1182380,"uid":148987,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<br />\n奶共丫拿"},{"pid":"98d9b6cd8fd6b7d4eb229e27ed51db107739f54f","tid":1182380,"uid":27935,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90e1420cae3b0975940f91833741b25f2748656b","tid":1182380,"uid":98692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"肯定之前好似班bt狗，喺咁用，當唔洗流量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no